name: Sword & Shield Elite Trainer Box [Zacian]
cleanName: Sword and Shield Elite Trainer Box Zacian
extCardText:
A new era in the Pokemon Trading Card Game is here with the debut of the Pokemon TCG: Sword & Shield expansion. This Elite Trainer Box is a great way to start your collection of Galar region Pokemon. This collector's box will get your collection started off right with eight Sword & Shield booster packs, a selection of Energy cards, and 65 card sleeves featuring the Legendary Pokemon Zacian or Zamazenta to keep your cards well protected. You'll also get accessories like dice and acrylic condition markers along with a player's guide filled with useful strategies and images of every card in the expansion. Both collectors and competitive Pokemon TCG players will find a lot to enjoy in the Pokemon TCG: Sword & Shield Elite Trainer Box!

Contents:
• 8 Pokemon TCG: Sword & Shield booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Zacian
• 45 Pokemon TCG Energy cards
• A player's guide to the Sword & Shield expansion
• 6 damage-counter dice
• 1 competition-legal coin-flip die
• 2 acrylic condition markers
• A collector's box to hold everything, with 4 dividers to keep it organized
• A code card for the Pokemon Trading Card Game Online

name: Spring 2020 Collector's Chest Tin
extCardText:
Prepare for a trip to the Galar region in the Pokemon Trading Card Game with a Collector Chest that contains a variety of cool goodies fans will love. This Pokemon TCG: Collector Chest includes three foil promo cards highlighting each of the Galar region's first partner Pokemon: Grookey, Scorbunny, and Sobble. It also comes with five Pokemon TCG booster packs to add to your collection and a mini portfolio that can hold your favorite cards. Additional items like sticker sheets, a Pokemon notepad, and a coin featuring the first partner trio add to the fun. To top it off, everything comes packed in a sturdy metal case decorated with images of the Legendary Pokemon Zacian and Zamazenta.
This product contains
3 Promotional Promos of Grookey, Scorbunny and Sobble
5 Booster Packs
A Coin
A Notepad
A Mini Portfolio

name: Sword & Shield Elite Trainer Box [Set of 2]
cleanName: Sword and Shield Elite Trainer Box Set of 2
extCardText:
A new era in the Pokemon Trading Card Game is here with the debut of the Pokemon TCG: Sword & Shield expansion. This Elite Trainer Box is a great way to start your collection of Galar region Pokemon. This collector's box will get your collection started off right with eight Sword & Shield booster packs, a selection of Energy cards, and 65 card sleeves featuring the Legendary Pokemon Zacian or Zamazenta to keep your cards well protected. You'll also get accessories like dice and acrylic condition markers along with a player's guide filled with useful strategies and images of every card in the expansion. Both collectors and competitive Pokemon TCG players will find a lot to enjoy in the Pokemon TCG: Sword & Shield Elite Trainer Box!

Contents:
• 8 Pokemon TCG: Sword & Shield booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Zamazenta
• 45 Pokemon TCG Energy cards
• A player's guide to the Sword & Shield expansion
• 6 damage-counter dice
• 1 competition-legal coin-flip die
• 2 acrylic condition markers
• A collector's box to hold everything, with 4 dividers to keep it organized
• A code card for the Pokemon Trading Card Game Online
